  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Working together to protect UK leadership on aid and development</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is a three-year project to harness the power of strategically-driven, united action by UK NGOs to meet the challenges and grasp the opportunities of this critical period. Bond&#x2019;s activities will include: convening proactive, action-orientated coalitions; distilling and deploying a clear, compelling joint case for support for ODA to policy-makers and the public; and building support amongst policy-makers and the media to sustain and secure concrete policy commitments for more and better UK and EU ODA.</narrative>
  </description>
